      <h1>2,621 million litres saved</h1>
      <p>That’s how much water 44,327 people would drink in their lifetime.</p>
    </div>
  <%= image_tag "carbon_save.png", style: "width: 200px;" %>
    <div class="info-text">
      <h1>26,857 tonnes saved</h1>
      <p>That’s enough energy to power 6,140 houses for a year.</p>
    </div>
<div style="padding-bottom: 25px;"></div>
</div>
